events.name: Maker Faire 2016 Meetup Session 2
events.description:
Calling all Makers! This year's Maker Faire is right around the corner! If you would like to know how you can join in the fun, sign up for this Makers Meetup!

We invite everyone to come for this meet-up to join the lead Makers for ideation and helping to make this Maker Faire booth the best one yet! 

The ideas that have been selected so far are:

Human Hamster Wheel (Annabelle)
Bucket List Hologram (Mark)
Plastic Injection Machine (Arvin)
Musical Stairs + Shady Umbrella (Saad)
Modular Hovercraft (Kartikey)
Cotton Candy Shooter (Gabriel)
White / Blacksmith (Lev)
Powering a wheelchair (Peter)

There will be a presentation from the lead makers and this will be a call for volunteers to join in their projects! If you can't make it for this event, you can still sign up as volunteer for Maker Faire here: http://goo.gl/forms/XAvKjXQmqN

Details:
Maker Faire 2016 Meet up!
Date: 5th May, Thursday, 7pm
Venue: The Prototyping Lab @ NDC

Maker Faire will be happening on the 25th and 26th of June at the Singapore University of Technology and Design (SUTD) 
8 Somapah Road, Singapore 48737
